Note: trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HB introduces a buffer time after pressing down on the HomeButton
to ensure that Stimulus is not presented unless the finger has rested on the Homebutton for 
values.isi 
* HB label changes color to blue
* if the finger stays on HomeButton (no 'up' response detected) for values.isi time
then trial.ChoiceRTpracticepractice2 is called
* if the finger is lifted off too early from HomeButton, trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HBdown_repeat is called

<trial ChoiceRTpractice_HB>
/ ontrialbegin = [
	if (values.repeat == 0){
		values.responseArea = "";
		values.trialcount += 1;
		values.valid = 1;
		values.stimPresentTime = "";
		values.isi = list.isi_ChoiceRTpractice.nextValue;
		values.countUp = 0;
		values.count_earlyResponses = 0;
		values.rt = "";	
		values.rt_down1 = values.rt_down3;
		values.rt_down3 = "";
		values.rt_down2 = "";
		values.rt_up1 = "";
		values.rt_up2 = "";	
	
		values.targetPosition = list.targetbuttons_ChoiceRT.nextValue;
		if (values.targetPosition == 1) {
			shape.target.hposition = shape.1.hposition;
			shape.target.vposition = shape.1.vposition;			
		} else if (values.targetPosition == 2){
			shape.target.hposition = shape.2.hposition;
			shape.target.vposition = shape.2.vposition;		
		} else if (values.targetPosition == 3){
			shape.target.hposition = shape.3.hposition;
			shape.target.vposition = shape.3.vposition;				
		} else if (values.targetPosition == 4){
			shape.target.hposition = shape.4.hposition;
			shape.target.vposition = shape.4.vposition;			
		} else if (values.targetPosition == 5){
			shape.target.hposition = shape.5.hposition;
			shape.target.vposition = shape.5.vposition;				
		}	
	}	
]	
/ stimulustimes = [0 = HomeButton_ChoiceRT, HomeButtonLabel2_ChoiceRT, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
/ validresponse = (lbuttonup)
/ responseinterrupt = immediate
/ beginresponsetime = -1
/ timeout = values.isi
/ ontrialend = [
	trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HB.resetStimulusFrames();	
]
/ branch = [
	if (trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HB.response == 0 || monkey.monkeyMode){
		return trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HBoffSTIMdown;
	} else {
		return trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HBdown_repeat;
	}
]
/ recorddata = false
/ responsemessage = ("lbuttonup", HomeButtonLabel_ChoiceRT, 0)
/ responsemessage = (0,	ChoiceRT_feedbackEraser, 0)
</trial>

Note: trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HBdown_repeat waits once more for a HomeButton touchdown
- home button label changes back to white
- values.rt_down1 is updated to reflect the new HomeButton touchdown 
- if no touchdown occurs within 5000ms, a reminder/error message is presented
- once the touchdown occurs, trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HB is called once more

<trial ChoiceRTpractice_HBdown_repeat>
/ ontrialbegin = [
	values.repeat = 1;
	values.selectFeedback = 4;
	trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HBdown_repeat.insertStimulusTime(text.ChoiceRT_feedback, parameters.homeButton_RW);
]
/ stimulusframes = [1 = ChoiceRT_feedbackEraser, ChoiceRT_HBfeedback, homeButton_ChoiceRT, HomeButtonLabel_ChoiceRT]
/ validresponse = (homeButton_ChoiceRT)
/ responseinterrupt = immediate
/ beginresponsetime = -1
/ ontrialend = [
		trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HBdown_repeat.resetStimulusFrames();
		
		if (trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HBdown_repeat.response == "homeButton_ChoiceRT"){
				values.rt_down1 = script.elapsedTime;
				values.count_earlyResponses += 1;
		}
]
/ branch = [
	return trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HB;
]	
/ recorddata = false
/ responsemessage = ("homeButton_ChoiceRT", text.ChoiceRT_feedbackEraser, 0)
</trial>


Note: trial.ChoiceRTpractice is called after the homebutton is pressed for values.isi
- the Stim button appears
- collects script.elapsedTime when finger lifts off HomeButton after Stim presentation 
and turns the Home Button label back to white
- collects script.elapsedTime when finger touches down on Stim Button 
- values.finalACC stores whether the response was actually correct (=Stim Button was pressed within predetermined time frame and finger wasn't lifted of Home Button); 0 = finger went down elsewhere

<trial ChoiceRTpractice_HBoffSTIMdown>
/ ontrialbegin = [
	values.valid = 1;
	values.ACC = 0;
	values.finalACC = 0;
	
	if (values.practice == "demo"){
		trial.choiceRTpractice_HBoffSTIMdown.insertStimulusFrame(text.demoStimReminder, 1);
	}	
]
/ stimulustimes = [0 = target]
/ validresponse = (lbuttonup, lbuttondown)
/ beginresponsetime = -1
/timeout = parameters.stim_RW
/ isvalidresponse = [
	if (trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HBoffSTIMdown.response == "lbuttonup"){
			values.countUP += 1;
			values.rt_up1 = script.elapsedTime;
			values.rt_releaseHB = values.rt_up1 - shape.target.timestamp;				
			
	} else if (trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HBoffSTIMdown.response == "lbuttondown"){
		values.valid = 1;
	
		values.rt_down2 = script.elapsedTime;
		if (mouse.y >= expressions.targetStimButton_top && mouse.y <= expressions.targetStimButton_bottom && 
			mouse.x >= expressions.targetStimButton_left && mouse.x <= expressions.targetStimButton_right){

			values.responseArea = "Target";
			values.finalACC = 1;
			values.ACC = 1;

		} else {
			values.ACC = 2;
			values.responseArea = "elsewhere";
		}		
	}
	
	return (values.valid == 1);
]
/ correctresponse = (lbuttondown)
/ response = correct
/ errormessage = true(HomeButtonLabel_ChoiceRT, 0)
/ responsemessage = (lbuttondown, eraseButton_ChoiceRT, 0)

/ ontrialend = [
	trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HBoffSTIMdown.resetStimulusFrames();
	list.practiceCorrect.removeitem(5);
	list.practiceCorrect.insertItem(values.finalACC, 1);	
	
	values.stimPresentTime = shape.target.timestamp;
	if (values.finalACC == 1){
		values.rt = expressions.A + expressions.B;			
	}
			
	if (values.responseArea == ""){
		values.ACC = 3;
	}

]
/ branch = [
	if (values.responseArea == ""){
		values.selectFeedback = 3;
		return trial.ChoiceRTpractice_feedback;
	} else {
		return trial.ChoiceRTpractice_StimOFF;
	}
]
/ recorddata = false
</trial>

Note: trial
- collects second UP response (ideally finger lifts off the Stim button)
- if something other than the Stim button was pressed, trial.ChoiceRTpractice_feedback is called
<trial ChoiceRTpractice_STIMoff>
/ validresponse = (lbuttonup)
/ beginresponsetime = -1
/ isvalidresponse = [
	values.rt_up2 = script.elapsedTime;
	return (trial.ChoiceRTpractice_StimOFF.response == "lbuttonup");
]
/ ontrialend = [
	values.countUP += 1;
]
/ branch = [
	if (values.responseArea == "elsewhere"){
		values.selectFeedback = 1;
		return trial.ChoiceRTpractice_feedback;
	} else {
		return trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HBdown;
	}
]
/ recorddata = false
</trial>


<trial ChoiceRTpractice_feedback>
/ stimulusframes = [1 = clearScreen, ChoiceRT_feedback]
/ trialduration = parameters.feedback
/ recorddata = false
/ branch = [
	return trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HBdown;
]
</trial>

Note: this trial collects the down response on the homebutton after the finger is lifted off the stim button;
if more trials need to be run it calls trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HB;
<trial ChoiceRTpractice_HBdown>
/ontrialbegin = [
	values.repeat = 0;
	values.selectFeedback = 4;
	trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HBdown.insertStimulusTime(text.ChoiceRT_feedback, parameters.homeButton_RW);
]
/ stimulusframes = [1 = ChoiceRT_feedbackEraser,homeButton_ChoiceRT, HomeButtonLabel_ChoiceRT, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, instructionReminder]
/ beginresponsetime = -1
/ validresponse = (homeButton_ChoiceRT)
/ isvalidresponse = [
	if (trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HBdown.response == "homeButton_ChoiceRT") {
		values.rt_down3 = script.elapsedTime;
	}
	return (trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HBdown.response == "homeButton_ChoiceRT");
]
/ responseinterrupt = immediate
/ ontrialend = [
		trial.ChoiceRTpractice_HBdown.resetStimulusFrames();
		
		text.instructionReminder.textcolorblue = 166;
		text.instructionReminder.textcolorgreen = 166;
		text.instructionReminder.textcolorred = 166;
		
		if (list.practiceCorrect.mean >= 1 || monkey.monkeyMode){
			values.stopChoiceRTPractice = 1;
		}
]
/ recorddata = true
/ responsemessage = ("homeButton_ChoiceRT", text.ChoiceRT_feedbackEraser, 0)
</trial>


**************************************************************************************************************
**************************************************************************************************************
	BLOCKS
**************************************************************************************************************
**************************************************************************************************************

<block choiceRT_monitorSizeCheck>
/ skip = [
	(parameters.runAbsoluteSizes == false) || (expressions.screenHeight_inmm >= parameters.canvasHeight_in_mm);
]
/ trials = [
	1 = choiceRT_monitorSizeCheck;
]
/ onblockend = [
	script.abort();
]
</block>

<block choiceRT_intro>
/ onblockbegin = [
	values.practice = "demo";
	list.practiceCorrect.reset();
	values.trialcount = 0;
	text.instructionReminder.textColor = black;
]
/ trials = [
	1 = assembleTargetButtonList_choiceRT; 
	2= choiceRT_HBdemo; 
	3 = choiceRTpractice_HB; 
	4 = choiceRT_intro;
]
/ recorddata = false
</block>

<block choiceRT_practice>
/ onblockbegin = [
	values.practice = 1;
	list.practiceCorrect.reset();
	values.trialcount = 0;
	text.instructionReminder.textColor = black;
	values.stopchoiceRTPractice = 0;	
]
/ stop = [
	values.stopchoiceRTPractice == 1
]
/ trials = [
	1= choiceRTpractice_start; 
	2-10 = choiceRTpractice_HB;
]
/ onblockend = [
	list.isi_choiceRTpractice.reset();
	if (values.trialcount >= 10 && list.practiceCorrect.mean <1){
		values.practicePass = 0;
		values.practicePass_choiceRT = 0;
	}
]
</block>

<block choiceRT>
/ skip = [
	(values.practicePass == 0 && !monkey.monkeyMode);
]
/ onblockbegin = [
	values.choiceRTDuration = script.elapsedTime;
	values.practice = 0;
	values.trialcount = 0;
	list.latencies_choiceRT.reset();
	text.instructionReminder.textColor = black;
	list.targetbuttons_choiceRT.resetSelection();
]
/ trials = [
	1 = choiceRT_intro; 
	2 = choiceRT_start;
]
/ onblockend = [
	list.isi_choiceRT.reset();
]
</block>


<block choiceRT_end>
/ onblockbegin = [
	values.choiceRTDuration = script.elapsedTime - values.choiceRTDuration;
]
/ trials = [1 = finish]
</block>

**************************************************************************************************************
**************************************************************************************************************
	EXPERIMENT 
**************************************************************************************************************
**************************************************************************************************************

<expt crt>
/ blocks = [
	1 = choiceRT_monitorSizeCheck;
	2 = choiceRT_intro;
	3 = choiceRT_practice;
	4 = choiceRT;
	5 = choiceRT_end;
]
</expt>

**************************************************************************************************************
												End of File
**************************************************************************************************************